title: CLASSIC: Space cadet … err … feminist Brianna Wu trips all over her own smug attack on Milo
text:
CLASSIC: Space cadet … err … feminist Brianna Wu trips all over her own smug attack on Milo Posted at 2:39 pm on February 23, 2017 by Sam J. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
Feminist and Democratic candidate for congress Brianna Wu says the Left holds themselves to a higher standard … BAHAHA! There is no equivalent of Milo on the left because we hold ourselves to higher standards. Our Milo wannabes get ostracized pretty quickly. 
— Brianna Wu (@Spacekatgal) February 22, 2017 
Oh man. 
Ok, so most people on the right disagreed with and even condemned Milo for allegedly attempting to normalize pedophilia. And he was also disinvited from CPAC, lost his book deal and then ended up resigning from Breitbart. 
That would tell you that even if Milo was a conservative (he’s not), people on the right ostracized him pretty quickly. 
The Left seems to protect their own horrible people. 
— David Edward (@_David_Edward) February 22, 2017 
Oops. @Spacekatgal Higher standard? You Lefties had a Women's March dedicated to taxpayer funded abortion. Your entire party is Milo. 
— Stewart Hanson (@Jaystew17) February 22, 2017 Trending
